POST запрос:
curl -X 'POST' 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks' -H 'accept: application/json' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"name": "task5"}'

PUT запрос:
curl -X 'PUT' 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks/3' -H 'accept: application/json' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"name": "delotri"}'

DELETE запрос:
curl -X 'DELETE' 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks/3' -H 'accept: application/json' 